    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/c58b12293d25919fab186fca0fcf0ad2.poster.avif?t=1723130795\" width=688 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/c58b12293d25919fab186fca0fcf0ad2.webm?t=1723130795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/c58b12293d25919fab186fca0fcf0ad2.mp4?t=1723130795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>扮演意外进入蒸汽世界，成为一名“蒸汽萨满”的高三学生，在蒸汽驱动的计算机——“差分机”主宰的文明中冒险。失去了记忆、拥有雷电之力的机械萨满，需要在这趟旅程中找回自我与灵魂。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/e44e188e021daa06038d10c81bd021a6.poster.avif?t=1723130795\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/e44e188e021daa06038d10c81bd021a6.webm?t=1723130795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/e44e188e021daa06038d10c81bd021a6.mp4?t=1723130795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《灵魂差分》是一款蒸汽朋克的2D平台动作游戏，复杂庞大的差分机中有无数机关和怪物，在探索的过程中找回自己的记忆，发掘蒸汽文明中的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/f97e9f72f5d280dec7bede4a4eeadda3.poster.avif?t=1723130795\" width=686 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/f97e9f72f5d280dec7bede4a4eeadda3.webm?t=1723130795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/f97e9f72f5d280dec7bede4a4eeadda3.mp4?t=1723130795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><br>●具有浓厚机械特色的横版平台跳跃类游戏，并富有浓厚的文化内涵。<br><br>●蒸汽机械于萨满法术结合的技能树，一步步提升自己的力量。<br><br>●独特的“萨满鼓”武器系统，配合技能产生无穷无尽的组合，不再只是简单的跳跃。<br><br>●蒸汽时代独有的计算机--差分机，为游戏带来了蒸汽时代机械的特殊美感，浓烈的工业美学。<br><br>●神秘的萨满文化与雷电产生未知的碰撞，拥有多种能力的期望的你能否揭开灵魂树的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/dc5b51243c321badee758237f523adbe.poster.avif?t=1723130795\" width=688 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/dc5b51243c321badee758237f523adbe.webm?t=1723130795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146970/extras/dc5b51243c321badee758237f523adbe.mp4?t=1723130795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
